0.174   2021-07-10  Released-By: PERLANCAR; Urgency: medium

	- Better wrapping of usage line to adjust for the newer
	  Perinci::Sub::To::CLIDocData (0.297+) which does not use spaces
	  between alternation |.


0.173   2020-04-27  Released-By: PERLANCAR; Urgency: medium

	- Wrap potentially long usage line.


0.172   2020-02-06  Released-By: PERLANCAR; Urgency: medium

	- Don't require metadata to be already normalized, provide
	  meta_is_normalized option just like the others (e.g.
	  Perinci::Sub::GetArgs::Argv).


0.171   2019-04-15  Released-By: PERLANCAR

	- Observe argument spec property 'slurpy' in addition to 'greedy'
	  (Rinci 1.1.88).


0.170   2017-08-12  Released-By: PERLANCAR

	- Search description.alt.env.cmdline before description in meta.


0.16    2017-07-24  Released-By: PERLANCAR

	- [ux] When there is no summary, skip producing the whole line
	  because showing just the program name is not very useful.


